<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <title>System Administrator Invitation</title>
    <style>
      body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
      .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
      .header { background-color: #dc3545; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center; }
      .content { padding: 20px; background-color: #f9f9f9; }
      .button { display: inline-block; padding: 12px 24px; background-color: #dc3545; color: white; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px; margin: 20px 0; }
      .footer { padding: 20px; text-align: center; color: #666; font-size: 14px; }
      .admin-badge { background-color: #dc3545; color: white; padding: 4px 8px; border-radius: 4px; font-weight: bold; }
      .warning { background-color: #fff3cd; border: 1px solid #ffeaa7; padding: 15px; border-radius: 4px; margin: 15px 0; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <h1>🔐 System Administrator Invitation</h1>
      </div>

      <div class="content">
        <h2>You're invited as a <span class="admin-badge">System Administrator</span></h2>

        <p><strong><%= @inviter.name %></strong> has invited you to become a System Administrator.</p>

        <div class="warning">
          <strong>⚠️ Important:</strong> System administrators have full access to all organizations and system settings. This is a high-privilege role with significant responsibilities.
        </div>

        <p>As a System Administrator, you will be able to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Access and manage all client organizations</li>
          <li>Manage other administrators</li>
          <li>Configure system-wide settings</li>
          <li>Monitor system performance and usage</li>
          <li>Handle billing and subscription management</li>
        </ul>

        <p>Click the button below to accept your invitation:</p>

        <div style="text-align: center;">
          <a href="<%= @accept_url %>" class="button">Accept Admin Invitation</a>
        </div>

        <p><small>Or copy and paste this link into your browser:</small><br>
           <small><%= @accept_url %></small></p>

        <hr>

        <p><strong>This invitation will expire on <%= @expires_at.strftime("%B %d, %Y at %I:%M %p") %>.</strong></p>

        <p>If you don't want to accept this invitation, you can simply ignore this email.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="footer">
        <p>This system administrator invitation was sent by <%= @inviter.name %>.</p>
        <p>If you have any questions about this invitation, please contact the sender directly.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
